<title>Ka Kipahna Pen Hukdampa</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel lopina leh a hawihna cheng sangin,
 Muh ka nuom ie Lal Krista mel chu;
 Zehawtna puon silh in linglukhuk khu mahleh,
 A hawih pen ie khawvel lal sang in.

[V2]
 Aw, ka kipahna pen Hukdampa,
 Ka thamuonna pen leh ka kipahna Na hi;
 Phatna'n hung pak in ka lunggil ah,
 Tuoilo ding in kumsawt chan inle.

[V3]
 2. Hukdampa hehpihna hi kuoa gen thei ding?
 Ei hawl in gimtheih tin cheng A thuok;
 Bethlehem leh Kalvari tang ah ei hawl a,
 Ei pui kit tai hehpihna huong ah.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa Na hehpihna mel hawih ei muhsak in,
 Lungkham liengvai gimthei chate hih;
 Zie khawvel siesa nung hi ngaiin tau puong ie,
 Aw, Na ang lum ahin ei pawmin.
 4. Hung kit ding ahi lopina tawh meichung ah,
 A tatsate ei hung pui khawm di'n;
 Lei dahum I pawtsan-na ding ni a nai tai,
 Hallelujah ka kipak, Amen.</lyrics>
</song>